"{\"uid\": \"gbnews.com-sport-olympics-noah-lyles-mother-paris-olympics-security-200m-collapse\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Noah Lyles collapsed at the end of the 200m at the Paris Olympics earlier this week  GETTY  ByJack Otway,  Published: 11/08/2024  Updated: 11/08/2024  The 27-year-old recently won bronze in the 200m despite suffering from coronavirus  Noah Lyles' mother has accused Olympics security of 'refusing to call a doctor' after herson's collapse in the 200mearlier this week.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 99, \"end\": 104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Otway\", \"score\": 0.9319330253762387, \"rank\": 0.0729373761436366, \"text\": \"Otway\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Otway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Otway\"}, {\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old had gone into the event hoping to win his second gold of the games, having previously done so in the 100m last weekend.\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Lyles was forced to settle for bronze with the Team USA star later falling to the ground.Now, his mother Keisha Caine Bishop has alleged that stadium security initially refused to call a doctor for the sprinter.View this post on InstagramA post shared by Keisha Bishop (@keisha_caine_bishop)Writing on Instagram, she wrote: \\\"This was one of the scariest moments of my life!\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 516, \"end\": 521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9963216817912843, \"rank\": 0.0036824516224041965, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 563, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9997572868921137, \"rank\": 0.0002427266878230634, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keisha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\"}, {\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"score\": 0.999908104344621, \"rank\": 8.803354872930721e-05, \"text\": \"Bishop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keisha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\"}, {\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"score\": 0.999908104344621, \"rank\": 8.803354872930721e-05, \"text\": \"Bishop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Watching my son hold his chest gasping for air while the stadium security refused to call a Dr. as I begged them to send him help.\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They also refused to do anything to help.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They totally ignored me!\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No parent should ever have to experience this feeling of helplessness!\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"However, I want to thank the @nbcolympics team for helping me during this moment.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for seeing me & my son as human beings and not just another story.JUST IN:Jack Carlin update as Team GB star involved in horror cycling clash at Paris Olympics\\\"Words cannot express my gratitude for your empathy, professionalism, and kindness.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.6161608834736579, \"rank\": 0.6228591880641084, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}, {\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Carlin\", \"score\": 0.7998890933453702, \"rank\": 0.25017331567527307, \"text\": \"Carlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Carlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Carlin\"}, {\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999969849673085, \"rank\": 3.008968379540033e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1401